  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "360 Recruitment Consultant (Business Development)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>End to end recruitment for IT & Non IT Clients</li><li>Responsible for business development, focusing on Semi Conductor, healthcare & life science sector.</li><li>Develop and maintain relationships with new and existing clients to understand their recruitment needs.</li><li>Developing and demonstrating strong market knowledge – staying informed about key industry developments and growth areas.</li><li>Conduct detailed screening, candidate evaluation, and shortlist submissions</li><li>Manage interviews, feedback loops, negotiations, and successful closures</li><li>Act as the primary recruitment partner for assigned clients</li><li>Build deep, consultative relationships with hiring managers and HR stakeholders</li><li>Provide market intelligence, hiring insights, and advisory on talent strategies</li><li>Support business development conversations alongside account managers when needed</li><li>Conduct talent mapping for niche or hard-to-fill roles</li><li>Stay updated on market trends, sector hiring patterns, and competitor insights</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 6 years of experience in agency recruitment or executive search.</li><li>Minimum of Bachelors degree in business administration or similar relevant education background.</li><li>Proven track record in permanent & contract placements and handling 360 recruitment.</li><li>Experience in client mapping and generating leads.</li><li>Strong client-facing capability with experience managing hiring managers and HR stakeholders</li><li>Excellent communication, negotiation, and relationship-building skills.</li><li>Work in a KPI driven model to achieve set targets by the organization.</li><li>Ability to thrive in a fast-paced, target-driven environment.</li><li>Passion for delivering high-quality talent advisory and client experience.</li></ul><p><br />EA Reg. No. 25C2690 | EA License No. R1330510 | sumit.sambhi@tangspac.com</p>",
